Using Enumerations
How can Enumerations be used?
Using Enumerations

public enum Day {
    SUNDAY, MONDAY, TUESDAY, WEDNESDAY,
    THURSDAY, FRIDAY, SATURDAY 
}

package Enomeration;
public class DayofWeekRun {
	public static void main(String[] args){
		DayofWeek myday = DayofWeek.Thuesday;
		System.out.println(myday);
		myday=DayofWeek.valueOf("Monday");
		System.out.println(myday);
	}
}



Енумерацията се използва за непроменящи се неща
Можем да swich-ваме по енумерации

И да foreach-ваме
for(Day d: Day.values()){
 System.out.println(String.format("Days of week %s",d))
}